title: 73 Jordan Harbinger: How to Increase Confidence and Overcome Fear of Rejection
description:
This week on the School of Greatness podcast, Lewis Howes and Jordan Harbinger discuss the journey of cultivating a confident way of being.
It's a powerful one. To get the show notes and more valuable information about the two, we welcome you to www.lewishowes.com/73
author: podcast@schoolofgreatness.com (Lewis Howes)
